#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.desktop.in:3
#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.desktop.in:4
#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:7
msgid "Annotator"
msgstr "Annotator"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.desktop.in:5
#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:8
msgid "Communicate with images better"
msgstr "讓圖片溝通更有效率"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.desktop.in:14
msgid "annotator;image;annotate;"
msgstr "annotator;圖片;標註;註記;"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.desktop.in:18
msgid "Edit Clipboard Image"
msgstr "編輯剪貼簿圖片"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.desktop.in:22
msgid "Take Screenshot"
msgstr "擷取螢幕截圖"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:10
msgid "Trevor Williams"
msgstr "Trevor Williams"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:20
msgid "Welcome Screen"
msgstr "歡迎畫面"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:24
msgid "Annotation Editor"
msgstr "標註編輯器"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:28
msgid ""
"Communicate with images. Better. Open image files or take screenshots, add "
"various types of image annotations, and export the annotated image in a "
"number of image formats."
msgstr ""
"讓圖片溝通更有效率。開啟圖片檔案或擷取螢幕截圖，新增各種類型的圖片標註，"
"並將標註後的圖片匯出為多種圖片格式。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:33
msgid "Load image from the file system, clipboard or a screenshot."
msgstr "從檔案系統、剪貼簿或螢幕截圖載入圖片。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:34
msgid ""
"Add shapes, stickers, images, text, drawings, and other callouts to "
"highlight image details."
msgstr ""
"新增形狀、貼圖、圖片、文字、繪圖及其他標記來凸顯圖片細節。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:35
msgid "Save custom shapes for easy reuse."
msgstr "儲存自訂形狀以便重複使用。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:36
msgid "Add magnifiers to enhance image details."
msgstr "新增放大鏡以增強圖片細節。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:37
msgid "Blur out portions of the image to obfuscate data."
msgstr "模糊部分圖片以遮蔽資料。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:38
msgid "Crop, resize and add image borders."
msgstr "裁切、調整大小和新增圖片邊框。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:39
msgid "Control colors, line thickness and font details."
msgstr "控制色彩、線條粗細和字型細節。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:40
msgid "Built-in color picker to copy image pixel color to clipboard."
msgstr "內建顏色挑選器，可將圖片畫素色彩複製到剪貼簿。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:41
msgid "Zoom support."
msgstr "縮放功能。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:42
msgid "Unlimited undo/redo of any change."
msgstr "無限次復原/重做任何變更。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:43
msgid "Export to JPEG, PNG, TIFF, BMP, PDF, SVG and WebP image formats."
msgstr "匯出為 JPEG、PNG、TIFF、BMP、PDF、SVG 和 WebP 圖片格式。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:44
msgid "Support for copying annotated image to clipboard."
msgstr "可將標註後的圖片複製到剪貼簿。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:45
msgid "Support for dragging out a PNG image to another app or location."
msgstr "可將 PNG 圖片拖曳到其他應用程式或位置。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:46
msgid "Printer support."
msgstr "列印功能。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:61
#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:94
#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:124
#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:153
#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:172
#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:202
msgid "Changes"
msgstr "變更"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:63
msgid "Updated Italian translation (thanks to Albano Battistella)."
msgstr "更新義大利文翻譯（感謝 Albano Battistella）。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:65
#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:80
#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:102
#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:130
#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:158
#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:183
#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:213
msgid "Bug Fixes"
msgstr "問題修正"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:67
msgid ""
"Fixed issue with Annotator window not hiding during a screenshot (thanks to "
"Achille Leduc for fixing)."
msgstr ""
"修正擷取螢幕截圖時 Annotator 視窗未隱藏的問題（感謝 Achille Leduc 修正）。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:68
msgid ""
"Fixed issue with screenshotting on various systems (thanks to Achille Leduc "
"for fixing)."
msgstr ""
"修正在各系統上擷取螢幕截圖的問題（感謝 Achille Leduc 修正）。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:69
msgid "Fixed display issues with HiDPI and scaled displays."
msgstr "修正 HiDPI 和縮放顯示器的顯示問題。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:75
#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:88
#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:114
#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:149
#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:166
#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:193
msgid "New"
msgstr "新功能"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:77
msgid ""
"Added ability to zoom in and out using Control-Scrollwheel (thanks to Loric "
"Brevet)"
msgstr ""
"新增使用 Control + 滾輪放大和縮小的功能（感謝 Loric Brevet）"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:78
msgid ""
"Added ability to pan canvas with middle click and drag (thanks to Loric "
"Brevet)"
msgstr ""
"新增使用滑鼠中鍵拖曳來平移畫布的功能（感謝 Loric Brevet）"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:82
msgid "Fixed drawing issues with RTL languages and the text tool"
msgstr "修正 RTL 語言與文字工具的繪製問題"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:90
msgid "Added ability to export to an editable Annotator file."
msgstr "新增匯出為可編輯 Annotator 檔案的功能。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:91
msgid "Added support for WebP export."
msgstr "新增 WebP 匯出功能。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:92
msgid "Added about window."
msgstr "新增關於視窗。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:96
msgid "Updated screenshot to use D-Bus capture mechanism."
msgstr "更新螢幕截圖以使用 D-Bus 擷取機制。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:97
msgid "Removed references to gtk3 in build files."
msgstr "移除建置檔案中對 gtk3 的參照。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:98
msgid "Improved export menu UI."
msgstr "改善匯出選單介面。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:99
msgid "Updated issues with GitHub continuous improvement action."
msgstr "更新 GitHub 持續整合動作的問題。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:100
msgid "Removed Debian packaging files."
msgstr "移除 Debian 打包檔案。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:104
msgid "Fixed default export values."
msgstr "修正預設匯出值。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:105
msgid "Fixed display issue for Flatpak."
msgstr "修正 Flatpak 的顯示問題。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:106
msgid "Fixed text copy/paste button functionality from format bar."
msgstr "修正格式列中文字複製/貼上按鈕的功能。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:107
msgid ""
"Fixed cursor display when Control key is pressed when in text edit mode."
msgstr ""
"修正文字編輯模式下按住 Control 鍵時游標顯示的問題。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:108
msgid "Fixed issues with application desktop actions."
msgstr "修正應用程式桌面動作的問題。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:116
msgid "Added option for transparent PNG export (thanks for Peter Willemsen)."
msgstr "新增透明 PNG 匯出選項（感謝 Peter Willemsen）。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:117
msgid "Added support for adding custom stickers."
msgstr "新增自訂貼圖功能。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:118
msgid "Added support for inserting images."
msgstr "新增插入圖片功能。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:119
msgid ""
"Added support for color picker (copy value to clipboard or change current "
"annotation object color)."
msgstr ""
"新增顏色挑選器功能（可將色彩值複製到剪貼簿或變更目前標註物件的顏色）。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:120
msgid "Added support for inserting speech and thought bubble shapes."
msgstr "新增插入對話泡泡和思考泡泡形狀的功能。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:121
msgid "Added ability to annotate image by drag/drop on welcome screen."
msgstr "新增在歡迎畫面拖放圖片進行標註的功能。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:122
msgid ""
"Added ability to drag a copy of the annotated image via a new \"PNG\" icon "
"in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"新增透過工具列中的「PNG」圖示拖曳標註圖片副本的功能。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:126
msgid "Converted codebase from GTK3 to GTK4."
msgstr "將程式碼基礎從 GTK3 轉換為 GTK4。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:127
msgid "Updated Flatpak platform from 7.2 to 8."
msgstr "將 Flatpak 平台從 7.2 更新至 8。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:128
msgid "Improving look of toolbar dropdowns."
msgstr "改善工具列下拉選單外觀。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:132
msgid ""
"Fixed issue where boolean export values were not properly saving (thanks to "
"Peter Willemsen)."
msgstr ""
"修正布林匯出值無法正確儲存的問題（感謝 Peter Willemsen）。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:133
msgid ""
"Fixed issue with duplicating canvas items by holding Control while dragging "
"an item."
msgstr ""
"修正按住 Control 鍵拖曳物件以複製畫布物件的問題。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:134
msgid ""
"Fixed issues with missing icons on non-elementary distributions (thanks to "
"Kevin Ernst)."
msgstr ""
"修正非 elementary 發行版上圖示遺失的問題（感謝 Kevin Ernst）。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:135
msgid "Fixed issue with certain icons not displaying properly in dark mode."
msgstr "修正部分圖示在深色模式下無法正確顯示的問題。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:136
msgid "Fixed issue with icons being installed in the wrong place."
msgstr "修正圖示安裝到錯誤位置的問題。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:137
msgid "Fixed issue with dismissing popover when the export button is clicked."
msgstr "修正按下匯出按鈕時彈出框未關閉的問題。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:138
msgid "Fixed issue with the --use-clipboard command-line option."
msgstr "修正 --use-clipboard 命令列選項的問題。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:139
msgid ""
"Fixed application crash issue in some cases when annotate items are deleted."
msgstr ""
"修正刪除標註物件時在某些情況下應用程式當機的問題。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:140
msgid "Fixed issues with using the screenshot capture functionality."
msgstr "修正使用螢幕截圖擷取功能的問題。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:141
msgid "Fixed issue with canvas scrolling in various cases."
msgstr "修正各種情況下畫布捲動的問題。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:142
msgid "Fixed display issues with icons in dark modes."
msgstr "修正深色模式下圖示的顯示問題。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:143
msgid "Fixed issue with the font icon not appearing correctly on some systems."
msgstr "修正字型圖示在部分系統上無法正確顯示的問題。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:151
msgid "Added Russian translation (thanks to @lenemter)."
msgstr "新增俄文翻譯（感謝 @lenemter）。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:155
msgid "Updated Italian translations (thanks to @albanobattistella)."
msgstr "更新義大利文翻譯（感謝 @albanobattistella）。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:156
#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:174
msgid "Updated Dutch translation (thanks to Heimen Stoffels)."
msgstr "更新荷蘭文翻譯（感謝 Heimen Stoffels）。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:160
msgid ""
"Fixed translation string issues related to Zoom and Screenshot (thanks to "
"@lenemter)."
msgstr ""
"修正與縮放和螢幕截圖相關的翻譯字串問題（感謝 @lenemter）。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:168
msgid ""
"Adding support for taking screenshots from within the application (screen, "
"window and area)."
msgstr ""
"新增從應用程式內擷取螢幕截圖的功能（全螢幕、視窗和區域）。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:169
msgid "Adding command-line options for taking screenshots."
msgstr "新增擷取螢幕截圖的命令列選項。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:170
msgid "Adding support for creating and saving custom arrows and shapes."
msgstr "新增建立和儲存自訂箭頭與形狀的功能。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:175
#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:204
msgid "Updated Italian translation (thanks to @albanobattistella)."
msgstr "更新義大利文翻譯（感謝 @albanobattistella）。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:176
msgid "Updated Flatpak SDK from version 6 to 6.1."
msgstr "將 Flatpak SDK 從版本 6 更新至 6.1。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:177
msgid "Modified .gitignore to ignore .swp files from anywhere in the codebase."
msgstr "修改 .gitignore 以忽略程式碼庫中任何位置的 .swp 檔案。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:178
msgid "Changed shape dropdown to display four shapes per row instead of two."
msgstr "將形狀下拉選單改為每列顯示四個形狀而非兩個。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:179
msgid "Enhanced export UI and adding export options for PNG and JPEG types."
msgstr "增強匯出介面並新增 PNG 和 JPEG 類型的匯出選項。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:180
msgid ""
"Changed JPEG export to use both .jpeg and .jpg file extensions (defaults to ."
"jpg now)."
msgstr ""
"將 JPEG 匯出改為同時使用 .jpeg 和 .jpg 副檔名（現預設為 .jpg）。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:181
msgid "Improved arrow icon in toolbar."
msgstr "改善工具列中的箭頭圖示。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:185
msgid "Improved ability to click on shapes that only have borders."
msgstr "改善點選僅有邊框形狀的操作體驗。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:186
msgid "Fixed issues with copying the contents of one shape into another."
msgstr "修正在形狀之間複製內容的問題。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:187
msgid ""
"Fixed issue with displaying star and line icons in shapes toolbar for dark "
"mode."
msgstr ""
"修正深色模式下形狀工具列中星形和線條圖示的顯示問題。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:195
msgid ""
"Added keyboard shortcuts for creating annotation items, printing and "
"displaying contextual menus."
msgstr ""
"新增建立標註物件、列印及顯示右鍵選單的鍵盤快速鍵。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:196
msgid "Added keyboard shortcut cheatsheet."
msgstr "新增鍵盤快速鍵速查表。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:197
msgid "Added keyboard shortcut support for non-English keyboards."
msgstr "新增非英文鍵盤的快速鍵支援。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:198
msgid "Added Brazilian Portuguese translation (thanks to Fúlvio Alves)."
msgstr "新增巴西葡萄牙文翻譯（感謝 Fúlvio Alves）。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:199
msgid "Added Slovak translation (thanks to @MartinIIOT)"
msgstr "新增斯洛伐克文翻譯（感謝 @MartinIIOT）"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:200
msgid ""
"Added support for hitting the escape key to deselect all items on the canvas."
msgstr ""
"新增按下 Escape 鍵取消選取畫布上所有物件的功能。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:205
msgid "Updated German translation (thanks to Hannes Fritz)."
msgstr "更新德文翻譯（感謝 Hannes Fritz）。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:206
msgid "Updated zoom UI to make it more consistent with other elementary apps."
msgstr "更新縮放介面以與其他 elementary 應用程式更一致。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:207
msgid "Improved accuracy of the list of translatable files."
msgstr "改善可翻譯檔案清單的正確性。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:208
msgid "Moved arrow annotation to its own button in the toolbar."
msgstr "將箭頭標註移至工具列中的獨立按鈕。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:209
msgid ""
"Removed Accounts permissions from Flatpak manifest as it is no longer needed."
msgstr ""
"從 Flatpak manifest 中移除已不再需要的帳號權限。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:210
msgid "Removed text grab selector when editing text."
msgstr "移除編輯文字時的文字抓取選擇器。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:211
msgid ""
"Changed behavior of Return key when text is edited to keep the text item "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"變更編輯文字時 Return 鍵的行為，使文字物件保持選取狀態。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:215
msgid "Fixed icons8_cup sticker issue (thanks to Jan Tojnar)."
msgstr "修正 icons8_cup 貼圖問題（感謝 Jan Tojnar）。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:216
msgid ""
"Fixed issue where the toolbar state did not update to match the currently "
"selected item."
msgstr ""
"修正工具列狀態未隨目前選取物件更新的問題。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:217
msgid ""
"Fixed issue where dragging a blur rectangle outside of the image caused "
"application crash."
msgstr ""
"修正將模糊矩形拖曳到圖片外部導致應用程式當掉的問題。"

#: data/com.github.phase1geo.annotator.appdata.xml.in:218
msgid ""
